description:
Fabric Bedside Table 2 Drawers Grey

People sometimes wonder why they need a bedside table. The answer is simply because a good bedside table is extra storage space for your personal essentials, a spot for your table lamp, and of course, a place for your cuppa. And not least, a perfect companion to your bed.

Simply designed with elegant linen fabric, this bedside table is the perfect furniture to bring a modern style to your bedroom. The practical design consists of two large drawers, plenty of space to store your personal accessories and knick knacks. It features MDF panels with anti-rust coated metal draw runners and contemporary aluminium handles. An elite in quality and design, and a perfect addition to any home interior.

Too good to be used only in the bedroom? Well, you can also use the bedside table as a side table with drawers to complement your contemporary home decor . Whichever way you choose to use it, our Bedside Table is always the better side of design.

Features
* Elegant linen fabric
* Modern stylish design
* Solid MDF frame construction
* Contemporary aluminium handles
* Anti-rust coated metal draw runners
* Easy assembly

Specifications
* 2 Large Drawers
* Dimensions: 40 x 48.5 x 50
* Refer to gallery for further dimensions
* Colour: Grey

Package Contents
1 x Bedside Table
1 x Assembly Manual

This product comes with 1 year warranty
name: Artiss 1EA
